" Set style for gVim
hi SpellBad gui=undercurl
hi SpellBad ctermfg=red ctermbg=black 
hi SpellCap cterm=bold ctermfg=blue ctermbg=black

:nmap L J
:nmap H K
:nmap J 5j
:nmap K 5k

vnoremap Y "+y


